New Features\par
\cf0\b0\f1\lang1033\'a3\'ab\f0  Added Particle Nebula Visualizer. Swirling clouds, glowing bloom halos, and reactive trails create a cosmic, music\f4\_\f0 driven effect.\f1\par
\'a3\'ab\f0  Added Circular Spectrum Visualizer, a spoke\f4\_\f0 style frequency display radiating bars around a central ring, with configurable gain, smoothing, and weighting modes.\f1\par
\'a3\'ab\f0  Added Oscilloscope Visualizer, technical lines blazing across the screen, with stereo mode and glow trails.\f1\par
\'a3\'ab\f0  Added Classic Spectrum Analyzer Visualizer, made to feel like the classic Winamp spectrum bars.\par
\f1\'a3\'ab\f0  Added Star Field Visualizer, a gentle flow of stars set to music.\f1\par
\'a3\'ab\f0  Added settings for all new visualizers. Complete with sliders to set configurable variables in the visualizers. Saves with the other settings to the Windows Registry.\f1\par
\'a3\'ab\f0  Added Hyperspace Tunnel Visualizer. Colorful streaks coming at you.\par
\f1\'a3\'ab\f0  Added Fractal Cloud Visualizer. A Swirling mutating cloud.\par
\f1\'a3\'ab\f0  Added Waveform Visualizer. Oscilloscope style.\f1\par
\'a3\'ab\f0  Added RainbowBars Visualizer. A colorful dance of 30 bars with peak meters.\f1\par
\'a3\'ab\f0  New Visualizer System. Based on a contract interface with a modular host. New visualizers can be added easily.\f1\par
\'a3\'ab\f0  Added session stats to History & Statistics. Added progress bar for loading.\par
\f1\'a3\'ab\f0  Added various Lists and Charts to History & Statistics.\f1\par
\'a3\'ab\f0\lang9  Created a hidden DevTools form for viewing the raw History and Plays databases.\par
\cf1\b\fs28\par
\cf2\fs24 Improvements\par
\cf0\b0\f2\u10003?\f3\lang1033  Refactored to Visual Studio 2026. This involved some minor tweaking and style improvements. Still running on .NET 9.0. Planning to upgrade to .NET 10.0 in the coming months.\f5\lang9\par
\f2\u10003?\f3\lang1033  Refactored Visualizer system. Created a panel to dock the Visualizer Host. Removed old timer and picturebox system.\f5\lang9\par
\f2\u10003?\f3\lang1033  \f0 Refactored Meters to use NAudio instead of CoreAudio. Meters run at a 20fps rate with smooth drop offs.\cf2\b\lang9\par
\cf0\b0\f2\u10003?\f3\lang1033  Refactored tooltips throughout the app to overcome ToolTipEX's deficiencies. In some cases this meant strictly controlling ToolTipEX's life-cycle, in other cases completely swapping to another component. This should solve the disappearing tooltips issue.\f5\lang9\par
\f2\u10003?\f3\lang1033  Improved History & Statistics loading and data logic.\par
\f2\lang9\u10003?\f3\lang1033  Improved History & Statistics UI\f5\lang9\par
\f2\u10003?\f0  Began implementing a new tooltip system to avoid ToolTipEX implementation problems.\par
\cf1\b\fs28\par
\cf2\fs24 Fixes\par
\cf0\b0\f2\u10005?\f3\lang1033  Fixed potential crashing during History loading caused by concurrent background updates to history data.\f5\lang9\par
\f2\u10005?\f3\lang1033  Removed Core Audio because of conflicts with NAudio, which is needed for new Visualizer system.\f5\lang9\par
\f2\u10005?\f3\lang1033  Fixed various bugs in History & Statistics.\f5\lang9\par
\f2\u10005? \f3\lang1033 Fixed lyrics display error when loading plain text or metadata lyrics and published hotfix.\cf1\b\f0\fs28\lang9\par
